<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Auras International</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-fade-overlay"></div>
      <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="about-hero" class="hero-bg" />
    </section>

    <section class="about-section">
      <h1>Honouring Craft, Empowering Fashion</h1>
      <div class="about-container">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>
            Auras International is a two decade-old embroidery house based in
            Mumbai, India, specialising in high-quality beading and hand
            embroidery for global fashion brands. We combine deep industry
            expertise with a commitment to sustainable practices and
            international standard quality.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our clients value our collaborative approach and attention to detail
            at every step of the process—from design to delivery. At Auras, we
            pride ourselves on being a trusted partner for fashion houses
            seeking precision craftsmanship, reliable service and a modern,
            responsible supply chain.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <div class="img-back"></div>
          <img src="/images/hand-drawing.png" alt="Embroidery Drawing" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>

      <div class="core">
        <h3 class="core-values-title">Core Values</h3>
        <div class="core-values">
          <div class="value-box animate-up">
            <img src="/images/quality.png" alt="Quality" />
            <p>QUALITY</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-box animate-up">
            <img class="value-icon2" src="/images/precision.png" alt="Precision" />
            <p>PRECISION</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-box animate-up">
            <img class="value-icon3" src="/images/collabration.png" alt="Partnership" />
            <p>COLLABORATION</p>
          </div>
          <div class="value-box animate-up">
            <img class="value-icon4" src="/images/leaf.png" alt="Sustainability" />
            <p>SUSTAINABILITY</p>
          </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="about-section2">
      <div class="about-container2">
        <div class="about-image2">
          <div class="img-back2"></div>
          <img src="/images/hand-drawing2.png" alt="Embroidery Drawing" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-text2">
          <h1>The Team Behind The Craft</h1>
          <p>
            At Auras International, precision, passion and quality define us. Our skilled artisans and hands-on team
            work closely with clients from concept to delivery - ensuring consistent excellence, every time. Not only
            that - even our founder’s hand is on every part of the process.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our immense passion and strong drive for creative and competitive talent allow us to design and produce
            high-end exclusive beaded and embroidered work for our clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="founder-section">
      <div class="founder-container">
        <h2 class="founder-heading">About the Founder</h2>
        <p class="founder-text">
          Rooted in decades of couture craftsmanship, Auras International was founded by a creative visionary with a
          deep understanding of detail, discretion, and design. With an unwavering commitment to excellence, the founder
          has shaped Auras into a globally trusted partner for fashion houses seeking refined, hand-embroidered
          artistry. Every stitch carries the legacy of precision, passion, and quiet power, crafted to elevate brands
          without ever overshadowing them.
        </p>
        <div class="corner-squares">
          <div class="square small"></div>
          <div class="square large"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
      <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
      <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>